2 So I said he was 18. As I was giving him a massage, he was like how old are you. And then I was 18. But I kind of said it really fast because I didn't want to make it sound like I was lying or anything.
5 MP: So what other things did he ask you?
6 Um, how I know Haley, what school I went to.
7 MP: Did you tell him what school you went to?
8 Yeah but I told him Wellington. I didn't tell him Royal Palm.
9 MP: Did he ask you what grade you were in or did you tell him what grade you were in?
11 Yeah, he was like what grade are you in? Because I told him I was in 12th grade still.

15 MP: So you told him you were in 12th grade?
16 Yes.
17 MP: Are you sure?
18 Yes.

20 Um, that's about it. And he was kind of asking me like how I knew Haley, is Haley nice to me and then he told me how he knew Haley and he was like, I was kind of like, how do you know Haley. Cause I brought up the conversation. He said well I know Haley because she's been working for me for a long time. And
